	((Rotatable) bd).setRotation(BlockFace.EAST);
	b.setBlockData(bd);
	b.getState().update();
}
// now it&#39;s direction east
```
[BlockFace enum](https://hub.spigotmc.org/javadocs/bukkit/org/bukkit/block/BlockFace.html)

Also, if you have a [`WallSign`](https://hub.spigotmc.org/javadocs/bukkit/org/bukkit/block/data/type/WallSign.html), you will have access to this, so be sure it&#39;s a Sign and not a WallSign.

